     C* D14: PAGE field prints the page counter.
     FGDATA   IP  F    80              DISK
     FGOUT    O   F    132             PRINTER
     IGDATA       AA
     I                                     1   1   0DUMMY
     OGOUT    H  1  01
     O                                 10   'PAGE='
     O                         PAGE    12
     OGOUT    D  1  01
     O                                 10   'REC'
